      <title>英国游戏制造商将大规模裁员 90 名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/british-game-maker-supermassive-set-to-lay-off-90-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国视频游戏制造商 Supermassive Games 已通知 150 名员工，他们面临裁员“风险”，并将裁员约 90 人，这是游戏行业遭受的最新裁员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/british-game-maker-supermassive-set-to-lay-off-90-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 14:24:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
